<i>In favour:</i> 
</p>
<p>Angola, Bangladesh, Benin, Botswana, Burkina Faso, Chile, China, Congo, 
Costa Rica, Cuba, Djibouti, Ecuador, India, Indonesia, Jordan, Kuwait, 
Kyrgyzstan, Libya, Malaysia, Maldives, Mauritania, Mauritius, Mexico, 
Nigeria, Peru, Philippines, Qatar, Russian Federation, Saudi Arabia, Senegal, 
Thailand, Uganda, Uruguay 
</p>
<p><i>Against: 
</i>United States of America 
</p>
<p><i>Abstaining: 
</i>Austria, Belgium, Cameroon, Czech Republic, Guatemala, Hungary, Italy, 
Norway, Poland, Republic of Moldova, Romania, Spain, Switzerland] 
