Chile, China, Congo, Cuba, Djibouti, Ecuador, India, Indonesia, Jordan, 
Kuwait, Kyrgyzstan, Libya, Malaysia, Maldives, Mauritania, Mauritius, 
Mexico, Nigeria, Norway, Peru, Philippines, Qatar, Russian Federation, 
Saudi Arabia, Senegal, Switzerland, Thailand, Uganda, Uruguay 
</p>
