<p><b> H. Visits 
</b></p>
<p>42. At the 13th meeting, on 2 March 2012, the Secretary of State for Civilian Security, 
Democracy and Human Rights of the United States of America, Maria Otero, delivered a 
statement to the Human Rights Council. 
</p>
<p>43. At the 14th meeting, on the same day, statements in exercise of the right of reply 
were made by the representatives of China, the Democratic People&#8217;s Republic of Korea, 
Iran (Islamic Republic of) and Sri Lanka. 
