context of disaster settings 
</b></p>
<p>189. At the 52nd meeting, on 22 March 2012, the representative of Finland, also on 
behalf of Germany, introduced draft resolution A/HRC/19/L.4, sponsored by Germany and 
Finland and co-sponsored by Albania, Austria, Belgium, Bosnia and Herzegovina, Burundi, 
