<p><b>  Situation of human rights in Myanmar 
</b></p>
<p>305. At the 54th meeting, on 23 March 2012, the representative of Denmark introduced 
draft resolution A/HRC/19/L.30, sponsored by Denmark, on behalf of the European Union, 
