Union, and co-sponsored by Albania, Andorra, Australia, Bahrain, Botswana, Canada, 
Chile, Costa Rica, C&#244;te d&#8217;Ivoire, Croatia, Djibouti, Egypt, Georgia, Germany, Honduras, 
