Federation, United States of America; 
</p>
<p> (b) Representatives of observer States: Algeria, Brazil, Democratic People&#8217;s 
Republic of Korea, Egypt, France, Iran (Islamic Republic of), Morocco, Nepal, South 
Africa, Tunisia, Turkey, Venezuela (Bolivarian Republic of), Viet Nam; 
 (c) Observer for an intergovernmental organization: Council of Europe; 
 (d) Observers for non-governmental organizations: Action internationale pour la 
paix et le d&#233;veloppement dans la r&#233;gion des Grands Lacs, African Association of Education 
