<p>1014. At the same meeting, at the request of the representative of Libya, a recorded vote 
was taken on the first amendment introduced by the Russian Federation to draft resolution 
A/HRC/19/L.39/Rev.1. The amendment was rejected by 11 votes in favour, 16 against, 
with 19 abstentions. The voting was as follows: 
