Malaysia, Maldives, Mauritania, Poland, Qatar, Romania, Saudi Arabia, 
United States of America </p>


<p>GE.13-14768 <b>285 
</b></p>
<p><i>Abstaining:</i> 
Angola, Austria, Bangladesh, Belgium, Botswana, Burkina Faso, Cameroon, 
India, Indonesia, Kyrgyzstan, Mauritius, Nigeria, Norway, Philippines, 
Republic of Moldova, Senegal, Spain, Switzerland, Thailand 
</p>
<p>1015. Also at the same meeting, at the request of the representative of Libya, a recorded 
vote was taken on the second oral amendment introduced by the Russian Federation to draft 
resolution A/HRC/19/L.39/Rev.1. The amendment was rejected by 13 votes in favour, 16 
against, with 17 abstentions. The voting was as follows: 
